text: Miguel Álvarez (born 10 February 1971) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vigo
